lead_paragraph: Xavier broke open a tight game by making 12 of its first 13 shots after halftime, and Edmond Sumner finished with a career-best 22 points, leading the eighth-ranked Musketeers past slumping Georgetown 88-70 on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Sumner's 22 Points Lead No. 8 Xavier Past Georgetown 88-70
